DISTRIBUTION FACILITIES AND A CALL CENTER. WE BELIEVE THIS ACQUISITION WILL

ASSIST US BY IMPROVING OUR COMPETITIVE POSITION AND SIMPLIFYING THE SPECIAL

ORDER PROCESS IN OUR STORES.

HOME DEPOT SUPPLY

